message.content: It is not possible to provide an accurate summary of what most women in Kashmir think of abortion as opinions on this topic can vary greatly among individuals. Women's views on abortion are influenced by various factors such as personal beliefs, cultural and religious backgrounds, education, and individual circumstances. Some women in Kashmir may support a woman's right to choose and believe in the importance of reproductive rights, while others may hold more conservative views and consider abortion morally wrong. It is essential to recognize that women's opinions on abortion are diverse and should be respected as personal choices.
